{"tid":1677044,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"入黎話你知點解我地呢班港豬罷工未試過成功","createTime":"2019-10-26T21:56:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T08:42:50.000Z","uid":175453,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"36388de92833147fbbe6977df551ff5fc63241ea","tid":1677044,"uid":175453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T21:56:24.000Z","msg":"個個心態都仲係，得我罷有鬼用<br />\n個個都唔做 變左冇人做<br />\n所以 我地要諗方法成立<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全港最大形工會聯盟</span></span><br />\n<br />\n只要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">每個行業</span></span> 搵<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一定人數</span></span><br />\n<br />\n申請登記職工會<br />\n職工會須於成立後30 天內依照《職工會條例》的規定，向職工會登記局局長申請登記。<br />\n<br />\n規則<br />\n職工會須制定一份規則，其中須包括《職工會條例》附表二所列的所有事項。各規則不得互相矛盾，模糊不確，難於理解或與《職工會條例》的規定不符。<br />\n<br />\n發起人<br />\n職工會登記的申請，須由該職工會不少於7 名有表決權會員簽署。<br />\n<br />\n會員<br />\n職工會會員須經常在香港居住，及正從事或受僱於與該職工會有直接關係的行業、工業或職業。<br />\n職工會的發起人可聯絡職工會登記局。職工會登記局會就登記程序事宜，例如職工會的擬議的名稱、草擬規則等提供意見，以供發起人參考。辦理職工會登記手續毋須繳交任何費用。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\">詳情</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.labour.gov.hk/tc/labour/content3_1.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.labour.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Flabour%2Fcontent3_1.htm&d=HXPWCXSY8fSkht0R8v8uOQKWJX65Gw4YGtkQ1cmlXhw%3D&h=f345f915\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.labour.gov.hk/tc/labour/content3_1.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n唔該幫我推爆佢"},{"pid":"5586eb959fb189ce15f1d9ef1565d3cd3a5dc70a","tid":1677044,"uid":258571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T21:57:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c9d8e0edee888f4aad3908428164e9004737f4f8","tid":1677044,"uid":175453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T22:01:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"afbbc563aa05bf1011cff17c7182821f638a570c","tid":1677044,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r